{"tid":297833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我跌左個電話","createTime":"2017-06-25T19:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T05:03:16.000Z","uid":91069,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea1f9d005fe99ef32b9fb84f7dfca44b07879a4","tid":297833,"uid":91069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T19:42:41.000Z","msg":"2日前下晏5點我係巴士跌左個電話(自己大頭蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n發現唔見之後我就打過去<br />\n點知已經熄左機 <br />\n仲見到whatsapp上線時間係晚上9點鐘<br />\nwhatsapp過去係單tick<br />\n<br />\n我再打過去巴士總站 司機就話無啦<br />\n代表俾人執左了 執個個人仲入過我whatsapp<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我已經打定輸數 <br />\n上網搵定最平既電話 諗住買啦<br />\n幾千蚊走唔甩<br />\n(今個月parttime白做了)<br />\n最唔開心係 入面有好多珍貴既相未backup<br />\n無左就算第日影返 意義都唔同<br />\n咁都無計 鬼叫自己唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知第2日 奇妙既事發生了<br />\n佢last seen顯示11am <br />\n姐係佢開左機 同埋入過我whatsapp <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來佢whatsapp左我妹妹 <br />\n仲叫我打返俾佢 拎番部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我就去左佢番工既地方拎番部機<br />\n佢仲叫我 下次小心D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔知你叫咩名 不過都多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝你生活愉快 好人有好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實香港呢<br />\n仲有好多好人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efdfd27f9fb6d8d2657fabddbb94a24613a8fa5","tid":297833,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T19:43:48.000Z","msg":"下次小心啲啦"},{"pid":"3c57626097c0274a63b4a941ec353119827f74ca","tid":297833,"uid":4316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T19:43:59.000Z","msg":"你真係好好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fde2efa9a51494551456dfc8c615e43ae90eb2","tid":297833,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-